The paper discusses evolutionary algorithms for multimodal optimization, which is a subfield of optimization and search algorithms. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which specifically deals with evolutionary algorithms. Other relevant sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
